# Force LF on shipped shell/python hook payloads so their `#!/usr/bin/env bash` shebangs
# survive a Windows/WSL checkout (CRLF would break `bash\r`). See the skills' Prerequisites
# sections. Extension-less git hooks (e.g. post-commit) are pinned by name.
*.sh          text eol=lf
*.py          text eol=lf
post-commit   text eol=lf
commit-msg    text eol=lf
